PageCamel version 0.992
===================

PageCamel is an integrated webframework with background workers. It
does not need an external webserver.

PageCamel is designed to be used in a relativly save intranet environment,
where speed and easy of development take priority over absulote security.

This is an unstable and unfinished release - for production use, please wait till version
1.0.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

